      "comment": "TIGER ROCKS (8) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fourth (35.20) last time in a R/A FIN at this track. Has a good record here at this journey. Looks the one to beat on his best form. MOTOR CITY ROSSI (3) broke well and quickly mustered speed to win over the 570m at Traralgon two runs back then settled forward again when finishing third at this track last start. Can feature again. PAW NIMBUS (1) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing sixth (23.63) in a Special conditions H at Horsham. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from three starts. Should play a prominent role.",
